        <thead  ><tr  ><th align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin;border-top:solid thin' class='html-align-center' >PE</th><th align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin;border-top:solid thin' class='html-align-center' >Answer</th></tr></thead><tbody  ><tr  ><td align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-center' ><b>B</b></td><td align='left' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-left' >
No.</td></tr><tr  ><td align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-center' ><b>I</b></td><td align='left' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-left' >
No, brown sugar is not healthier than white sugar.</td></tr><tr  ><td align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-center' ><b>C</b></td><td align='left' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-left' >
Brown sugar is not significantly healthier than white sugar.</td></tr><tr  ><td align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-center' ><b>R</b></td><td align='left' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-left' >
Brown sugar is not significantly healthier than white sugar.</td></tr><tr  ><td align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-center' ><b>S</b></td><td align='left' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-left' >
No, brown sugar is not necessarily healthier than white sugar.</td></tr><tr  ><td align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-center' ><b>T</b></td><td align='left' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-left' >
Brown sugar is not significantly healthier than white sugar.</td></tr><tr  ><td align='center' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-center' ><b>S</b>, <b>T</b>, <b>R(C)</b></td><td align='left' valign='middle' style='border-bottom:solid thin' class='html-align-left' >
Brown sugar is not significantly healthier than white sugar.</td></tr></tbody>
      </table>



</div>
