            <div class="additional-content">
                <h2><a name="cite"></a>Share and Cite</h2>

                <div class="social-media-links" style="text-align: left;">
                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22Optimizing%20Large%20Language%20Models%3A%20A%20Deep%20Dive%20into%20Effective%20Prompt%20Engineering%20Techniques&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/3161048%3A%0A%0AOptimizing%20Large%20Language%20Models%3A%20A%20Deep%20Dive%20into%20Effective%20Prompt%20Engineering%20Techniques%0A%0AAbstract%3A%20Recent%20advancements%20in%20Natural%20Language%20Processing%20%28NLP%29%20technologies%20have%20been%20driven%20at%20an%20unprecedented%20pace%20by%20the%20development%20of%20Large%20Language%20Models%20%28LLMs%29.%20However%2C%20challenges%20remain%2C%20such%20as%20generating%20responses%20that%20are%20misaligned%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20question%20or%20producing%20incorrect%20answers.%20This%20paper%20analyzes%20various%20Prompt%20Engineering%20techniques%20for%20large-scale%20language%20models%20and%20identifies%20methods%20that%20can%20optimize%20response%20performance%20across%20different%20datasets%20without%20the%20need%20for%20extensive%20retraining%20or%20fine-tuning.%20In%20particular%2C%20we%20examine%20prominent%20Prompt%20Engineering%20techniques%20including%20In-Context%20Learning%20%28ICL%29%2C%20Chain%20of%20Thought%20%28CoT%29%2C%20Retrieval-Augmented%20Generation%20%28RAG%29%2C%20Step-by-Step%20Reasoning%20%28SSR%29%2C%20and%20Tree%20of%20Thought%20%28ToT%29%2C%20and%20we%20apply%20these%20techniques%20to%20leading%20LLMs%20such%20as%20Gemma2%2C%20LlaMA3%2C%20and%20Mistral.%20The%20performance%20of%20these%20models%20was%20evaluated%20using%20the%20AI2%20Reasoning%20Challenge%20%28ARC%29%2C%20HellaSwag%2C%20Massive%20Multitask%20Language%20Understanding%20%28MMLU%29%2C%20TruthfulQA%2C%20Winogrande%2C%20and%20Grade%20School%20Math%20%28GSM8k%29%20datasets%20across%20metrics%20such%20as%20BLEU%2C%20ROUGE%2C%20METEOR%2C%20BLEURT%2C%20and%20BERTScore.%20The%20experimental%20results%20indicate%20that%20the%20most%20suitable%20Prompt%20Engineering%20technique[...]" title="Email">
